    "name": "索拉丽斯炼成计划 Project Solaris",
    "steam_appid": 3002740,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002740/extras/470c3225fe3a7f2c3d1381db69fde5ed.avif?t=1770956439\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002740/extras_big/470c3225fe3a7f2c3d1381db69fde5ed.webp?t=1770956439 width=1560 height=780 /></span><strong>【索拉丽斯炼成计划 内容简介】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏讲述居住在魔法使之岛的少女“索拉丽斯”渴望成为一名合格的魔法使，并毅然踏上追寻自由之旅的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了实现她的梦想，请与可靠的小搭档“霍姆”培养感情，锻炼战术头脑，攻克艰难的考验吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002740/extras/0f7ee7a6f9adc4be33d3a8bd05ba5e6c.poster.avif?t=1770956439\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002740/extras/0f7ee7a6f9adc4be33d3a8bd05ba5e6c.webm?t=1770956439\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002740/extras/0f7ee7a6f9adc4be33d3a8bd05ba5e6c.mp4?t=1770956439\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家在游戏中将扮演索拉丽斯，与敌人交战时也负责指挥霍姆。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗指令通过 QTE（快速反应操作）来完成。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002740/extras/978d37fa0013318144bac7cae0bd5b02.poster.avif?t=1770956439\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002740/extras/978d37fa0013318144bac7cae0bd5b02.webm?t=1770956439\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002740/extras/978d37fa0013318144bac7cae0bd5b02.mp4?t=1770956439\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但不必担心！随着剧情推进和“信任度”提升，即使复杂的招式也将轻松发动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >两人之间的情谊会成为胜负的关键！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【亲手打造装备、钻研专属战术】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过“开店”与“战斗”积累资金，打造全新装备！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 索拉丽斯的装备：造价高、性能强，只要资金充足即可随时购入。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 霍姆的装备：造价低、可装备数量更多，但结果带有随机性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如何分配有限的资金，全凭你的策略选择！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据霍姆现有的招式，打造最强的装备吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002740/extras/f6d79b6e39b0b8067e34d49035976251.poster.avif?t=1770956439\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002740/extras/f6d79b6e39b0b8067e34d49035976251.webm?t=1770956439\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002740/extras/f6d79b6e39b0b8067e34d49035976251.mp4?t=1770956439\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【剧情发生在 100 天内】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你需要在 3 枚卡牌当中做出选择，决定当天的行动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002740/extras/564d80110f6a406c0e1a9460b294ee15.poster.avif?t=1770956439\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002740/extras/564d80110f6a406c0e1a9460b294ee15.webm?t=1770956439\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002740/extras/564d80110f6a406c0e1a9460b294ee15.mp4?t=1770956439\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗、休息、学习技能、赚取资金……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次抉择，都会影响最终试炼的走向！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择特定卡牌或达成条件，还能推进支线剧情！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将与不同角色邂逅，共同编织独属于你的故事——每一步抉择，都将引向不同结局！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【登场角色】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●年幼却才华横溢的老同学——特提娅</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●严厉而善良的母亲——克洛瓦洁</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●怕麻烦的店主——奥加斯特</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●对索拉丽斯与霍姆寄予厚望的贤者——梅尔希奥</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●以及正暗中筹谋的可疑人物……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>动用你的战术头脑，为两位主角谱写一段成功的冒险传奇吧！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
